              <row>
                <entry>Plus</entry>
                <entry>Minus</entry>
                <entry>Interesting</entry>
              </row>
              <row>
                <entry>If the money is managed well, the fund will increase.</entry>
                <entry>With the fluctuating economy the money could perhaps be worth less in a few years’ time.</entry>
                <entry>Maybe I can use the money to buy myself a motor-bike when I go to university.</entry>
              </row>
              <row>
                <entry/>
                <entry/>
                <entry/>
              </row>
              <row>
                <entry/>
