                <entry>Minus</entry>
                <entry>Interesting</entry>
              </row>
              <row>
                <entry>I need a holiday.</entry>
                <entry>It’s a lot of money to spend on a trip, and I should plan ahead.</entry>
                <entry>Maybe I can get a job while I’m overseas, and gain some valuable experience.</entry>
              </row>
